similar.title: Merak
similar.description: External nature line auxiliary battery with integrated 5W wireless charger. Housing in combination of natural cork and wheat straw materials. 5,000 mAh capacity and charge status indicator. Double USB output and Type C input. With large printing surface and presented in an attractive eco design box.   The capacities shown in all our external auxiliary batteries are real, all of them incorporating non-recycled, grade A batteries, with a service life of at least 500 charging cycles, and complying with CE regulations.   In addition, they are manufactured according RoHS standards, and in compliance with the following safety requirements:  Power bank overcharge protection system.  Complete discharge protection system, which increases the durability of the power bank.  Blocking system to prevent short circuits.  Constant charging transfer system, in accordance with the capacity of the target device.

data.title: Riken
data.description: Hygienic, antibacterial and anti-contact safety key ring, made of resistant ABS with a solid finishing. Specially designed to avoid touching public usage surfaces with your hands (door handles, switches, public use taps, ATMs). With comfortable cut-out for the finger and presented in an individual bag. Recommended for pad printing.  Products with antibacterial treatments are able to drastically reduce the bacterial levels present on the surfaces of the materials, thanks to the addition of permanent static microbial agents, with high effectiveness in inhibiting and preventing bacterial contamination.  Item according to the ISO 22196 standard, which determines the antibacterial activity in plastic materials and non-porous surfaces. This allows us to know the effectiveness of microbial inhibition that additives have on treated objects by means of a quantitave evaluation.
